item.title: Need help with teleport id's in 317
item.dc:creator: @arham_4 arham 4
item.description:
@arham_4 wrote:

If it’s a command, search in client.java for

if (command.startsWith("home"))

and change the coordinates.

For the spell search for

case 4140:

and you will see

c.triggerTele(3243+misc.random(1), 3520, 0);

.

EDITED

The

(3243+misc.random(1), 3520

is my home coordinates, change the

(3243+misc.random

(The 3243) to 3210 and

(1), 3520

to 3424.
